t: O vi prophet when vi popol divorce women vi ensure divorce interim fulfilled Vi mezur such interim precisely Vi reverence DI your Lord Ne evict them their hejm nor shall vi far life miserable them force them las sur their own ili commit proven adultery! These est di legx. Anyone transgresses di legx commits injustice himself. Vi neniam kon; maybe DI vol io bon ven this